---
import AnimatedWave from "./animated-wave.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="border-border border-t px-6 py-20 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
  <div class="max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="font-display mb-8 text-4xl md:text-5xl">About me</h2>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr,2fr] md:gap-12">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="inline-block">
          <span class="text-accent font-display text-2xl">
            Since Dec 2023
          </span>
          <div class="bg-accent/30 mt-1 h-0.5"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
          Working uninterruptedly as a Software Engineer
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-foreground/80 space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I&apos;m a Software Engineer based in Medellín, Colombia, with a
          passion for building robust, scalable systems. Throughout my career,
          I&apos;ve had the opportunity to{" "}
          <span class="text-foreground font-medium"
            >lead technical projects</span
          > from conception to deployment, working with diverse clients and challenging
          requirements.
        </p>

        <p>
          I thrive in environments where I can architect solutions that make a
          real impact. Whether it&apos;s designing cloud infrastructure on GCP,
          building performant web applications with Next.js, or crafting
          efficient backend services with Go and NestJS, I bring a{" "}
          <span class="text-accent font-display"> meticulous approach </span>{
            " "
          }
          to every project.
        </p>

        <p>
          Currently seeking remote opportunities with international teams where
          I can contribute my expertise in full-stack development and cloud
          architecture while continuing to grow as an engineer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {/* Decorative wave */}
  <div class="absolute -bottom-4 left-1/3 hidden w-72 opacity-10 md:block">
    <AnimatedWave variant="accent" delay={0.2} class="w-full" />
  </div>
</section>
